r1926 | adk0212 | 2010-01-17 10:58:34 -0500 (Sun, 17 Jan 2010) | 3 lines

Force use of generic_usb on FreeBSD 8.0 and higher. FreeBSD USB API was
changed in 8.0, so from now on we will use libusb.

